track.name: Mean Old World
comments: ER war einer der ersten, der elektrische Töne produzierte und damit eine Revolution in der Blues Szene entfachte !!! ER ist ein Meilenstein des Elektrischen Blues !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Amazingly advance music for when it was recorded.  Suire beats listening to Perry Como.

When I first saw Chuck Berry on tv in 1957 and he duckwalked to Maybelline with his Gibson behind his neck, I thought "wow, nobody has ever done this before!".  In 1997, I saw an old black and white, grainy video of T-Bone Walker duckwalking while playing the T-Bone Shuffle with his Gibson behind his neck. It was dated 1947!!!  Chuck Berry had a great influence to pass along to future generations.
Lovely jazz- tinged blues from T-Bone(2)
Clapton stealing this one comes to mind!
This is a mean old world, baby to live in by yourself
